{"MessageType":"message", "content":"Are you deliberately trying to frustrate me? I've explained this repeatedly. This isn't a negotiation; it's a simple transaction. You offer a price, I accept or decline. You keep asking the same questions, implying I'm hiding something. I'm not. I'm protecting my time and my effort. Put some skin in the game. What's your offer?"}
